---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.astro";
import Hero from "../components/Hero.astro";
import Section from "../components/Section.astro";
import SectionHeader from "../components/SectionHeader.astro";
import Button from "../components/Button.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Holistic Approach - Dr. Sita">
  <Navbar />

  <main>
    <Hero
      title="Holistic Approach"
      subtitle="Integrating mind, body, and spirit for comprehensive healing and wellness."
    />

    <!-- Overview Section -->
    <Section>
      <div
        class="bg-surface/30 rounded-[32px] p-12 border border-highlight-med/10 backdrop-blur-xl"
      >
        <SectionHeader title="Our Holistic Philosophy" class="mb-8" />
        <p class="text-xl text-subtle/90 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          At Dr. Sita's Mind Body Care, we believe in treating the whole person,
          not just symptoms. Our holistic approach combines traditional medical
          knowledge with complementary therapies to achieve optimal health and
          wellness. We understand that physical, emotional, and mental
          well-being are interconnected, and true healing requires addressing
          all aspects of health.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-12">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-display text-foam mb-4">
              Core Principles
            </h3>
            <ul class="space-y-4">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg text-subtle/90">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-foam mt-2.5"></div>
                <span>Integration of mind-body-spirit connection</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg text-subtle/90">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-foam mt-2.5"></div>
                <span>Evidence-based complementary therapies</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg text-subtle/90">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-foam mt-2.5"></div>
                <span>Personalized treatment plans</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg text-subtle/90">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-foam mt-2.5"></div>
                <span>Focus on prevention and wellness</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-display text-iris mb-4">Benefits</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-4">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg text-subtle/90">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-iris mt-2.5"></div>
                <span>Improved overall well-being</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg text-subtle/90">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-iris mt-2.5"></div>
                <span>Better stress management</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg text-subtle/90">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-iris mt-2.5"></div>
                <span>Enhanced emotional balance</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg text-subtle/90">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-iris mt-2.5"></div>
                <span>Sustainable health improvements</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Section>

    <!-- Treatment Methods Section -->
    <Section>
      <SectionHeader title="Our Treatment Methods" />
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8">
        <div
          class="bg-surface/30 rounded-[32px] p-12 border border-highlight-med/10 backdrop-blur-xl"
        >
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-display text-foam mb-6">
            Mindfulness and Meditation
          </h3>
          <p class="text-xl text-subtle/90 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Our mindfulness practices help you develop greater awareness, reduce
            stress, and improve emotional regulation. Through guided meditation
            and mindfulness exercises, you'll learn to stay present and manage
            anxiety effectively.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-8">
            <h4 class="text-xl font-display text-foam mb-4">
              Techniques Include:
            </h4>
            <ul class="space-y-4">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg text-subtle/90">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-foam mt-2.5"></div>
                <span>Breath awareness meditation</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg text-subtle/90">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-foam mt-2.5"></div>
                <span>Body scan meditation</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg text-subtle/90">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-foam mt-2.5"></div>
                <span>Loving-kindness meditation</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div
          class="bg-surface/30 rounded-[32px] p-12 border border-highlight-med/10 backdrop-blur-xl"
        >
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-display text-iris mb-6">
            Yoga and Movement Therapy
          </h3>
          <p class="text-xl text-subtle/90 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Our yoga programs combine physical postures, breathing exercises,
            and meditation to promote physical strength, flexibility, and mental
            clarity. Sessions are tailored to your comfort level and specific
            needs.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-8">
            <h4 class="text-xl font-display text-iris mb-4">Components:</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-4">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg text-subtle/90">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-iris mt-2.5"></div>
                <span>Gentle yoga sequences</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg text-subtle/90">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-iris mt-2.5"></div>
                <span>Pranayama (breathing exercises)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg text-subtle/90">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-iris mt-2.5"></div>
                <span>Restorative poses</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div
          class="bg-surface/30 rounded-[32px] p-12 border border-highlight-med/10 backdrop-blur-xl"
        >
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-display text-love mb-6">Acupuncture</h3>
          <p class="text-xl text-subtle/90 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Our evidence-based acupuncture treatments work by stimulating
            specific anatomical points to modulate pain pathways, reduce
            inflammation, and enhance the body's natural healing mechanisms.
            This therapeutic approach has been shown to regulate
            neurotransmitters and promote homeostasis, supporting both
            physiological and psychological well-being.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-8">
            <h4 class="text-xl font-display text-love mb-4">Benefits:</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-4">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg text-subtle/90">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-love mt-2.5"></div>
                <span>Stress and anxiety reduction</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg text-subtle/90">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-love mt-2.5"></div>
                <span>Pain management</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg text-subtle/90">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-love mt-2.5"></div>
                <span>Improved energy flow</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Section>

    <!-- Integration Section -->
    <Section>
      <div
        class="bg-surface/30 rounded-[32px] p-12 border border-highlight-med/10 backdrop-blur-xl"
      >
        <SectionHeader title="Integrative Approach" class="mb-8" />
        <p class="text-xl text-subtle/90 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Our treatments are carefully integrated to provide comprehensive care.
          We combine different modalities based on your specific needs and
          goals, ensuring a balanced and effective healing journey.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-display text-foam mb-4">Assessment</h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-subtle/90 leading-relaxed">
              Thorough evaluation of your physical, emotional, and lifestyle
              factors to create a personalized treatment plan.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-display text-iris mb-4">Treatment</h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-subtle/90 leading-relaxed">
              Combination of therapies tailored to address your specific
              concerns and support overall wellness.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-display text-love mb-4">Support</h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-subtle/90 leading-relaxed">
              Ongoing guidance and adjustments to ensure optimal results and
              sustainable health improvements.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <Section class="py-32">
      <div
        class="bg-surface/30 rounded-[32px] p-12 border border-highlight-med/10 backdrop-blur-xl text-center"
      >
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display text-text mb-8">
          Begin Your Healing Journey
        </h2>
        <p
          class="text-xl text-subtle/90 leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto"
        >
          Experience the transformative power of our holistic approach. Schedule
          a consultation to discover how we can support your wellness goals.
        </p>
        <Button href="/contact" color="love" icon="mdi:calendar">
          Schedule a Consultation
        </Button>
      </div>
    </Section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
